1986

1 hr 47 mins

Comedy

Watchlist

Where to Watch

The set of a comedy about the American Revolution, being filmed in a sleepy college town, plays host to a variety of feuds in this wry meta comedy , as the grumpy author of the story being re-created deals with both on-screen and personal dilemmas.
